After the NVDA Earnings, focus shifted towards US Macro Data (GDP, PCE, UMich) which may affect the FOMCs September Meeting. This was combined with uncertainty around France's confidence vote which elevated Implied Vols in the regions. Next will continue to be data packed in the US with ISM, JOLTS, Factory Orders and NFPs being the main event on Friday.
英伟达财报公布后，市场焦点转向可能影响美联储9月议息会议的美国宏观数据（GDP、PCE、密歇根大学消费者信心指数）。叠加法国信任投票带来的不确定性，欧洲地区隐含波动率随之抬升。本周美国仍将迎来密集数据发布，周五的ISM制造业指数、JOLTS职位空缺、工厂订单和非农就业数据将成为重头戏。
